title: iPod 1.1.4 Custom Firmware Release V2 (PWNED iPods Only)
description:
iPod Touch 1.1.4 Firmware for pre-PWNED iPod Touch.


Modifications:

Modified \\\"Extended Preferences\\\" Application.

Combined Video/Music \\\"iPod\\\" Application.

Springboard.app Patch to enable Extended Applications. (Maps, Notes etc.)

Includes standard payload of jailbroken filesystem and Installer.app	


Fixes Since V1:

Fix Mis-spelled Extended Settings Label

Removed Broken Keyboard and Lock Click Switches from \\\"General Preferences\\\"


Additions Since V1:

Created a new \\\"Statusbar\\\" List in General Preferences that includes Fake Carrier String, Fake Time String, and Numeric WiFi and Battery Display (Courtesy of BLACKWOLF)
